<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<chapter xml:id="Chapter-Determinants" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Determinants</title>

  <p>
    After completing this chapter, students should be able to do the following.
  </p>
  
  <objectives>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Find determinants using cofactor expansion along a row or column.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Interpret determinants as areas and volumes.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Describe how row operations affect the determinant.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Describe the significance when the determinant is zero. 
                </p>
            </li> 
            
            <li>
                <p>
                    Analyze the determinant of a product algebraically and geometrically.
                </p>
            </li> 
            
            <li>
                <p>
                    Solve a system of equations using Cramer's rule.
                </p>
            </li> 
            
        </ul>
</objectives>

